FT  14 AUG 92 / Observer: Shipshape
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
How times change. The last time that Merseyside was filled with sailing
ships Derek Hatton and his unpatriotic Militant chums controlled the
quayside.
At the official dinner for the crews, Hatton forbade proposal of the loyal
