<HEADLINE>
FT  14 AUG 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG weakened further with a fall in the gold price depressing
sentiment. The overall index lost 53 to 3,155 and the industrial index was
52 lower at 3,997. The gold index declined 43, or 4.4 per cent to 937.
</TEXT>
