FT  14 AUG 92 / UK Company News: Sea Containers shows improvement
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Sea Containers, the Bermuda-based container leasing, ferries and hotels
group, yesterday announced second quarter pre-tax profits down from Dollars
15.8m to Dollars 13.5m (Pounds 7m).
The result was struck on turnover up from Dollars 97m to Dollars 115.5m.
However, the figures for the corresponding period last time benefited from a
non-recurring Dollars 6.2m out-of-court settlement of a long-standing claim
