Keppel is one of a number of groups involved in discussions with the
Philippine authorities about leasing Subic Bay base, the former US naval
base north of Manila. Keppel wants to convert Subic Bay into a commercial
shiprepair yard and will soon put a formal proposal to the Philippines. The
US is due to complete its move out of Subic Bay by the end of the year.
