USX said the proceeds from the offering would be used for general business
purposes at its Marathon gas group of which the Delhi group had been part.
The effort to realise additional value for Marathon follows the company's
stock split last year, when USX agreed to issue a new class of stock after
coming under pressure from Mr Carl Icahn, the New York financier.
